{% layout 'theme' %}

<style>
  .hh-page { background:#080808; color:#f2ede1; font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif; min-height:60vh; }
  .hh-page-inner { max-width:780px; margin:0 auto; padding:80px 48px; }
  .hh-page h1 { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:42px; font-weight:400; color:#f2ede1; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .hh-page-rule { width:48px; height:1px; background:#C4A843; margin-bottom:48px; }
  .hh-page h2 { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:22px; font-weight:400; color:#f2ede1; margin:40px 0 16px; }
  .hh-page p { font-size:13px; color:rgba(242,237,225,0.55); line-height:1.9; font-weight:300; margin-bottom:16px; }
  .hh-page ul { padding-left:20px; }
  .hh-page ul li { font-size:13px; color:rgba(242,237,225,0.55); line-height:1.9; font-weight:300; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .hh-mat-badge { display:inline-block; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; color:#C4A843; text-transform:uppercase; border:1px solid #C4A843; padding:5px 12px; margin-bottom:24px; }
  @media(max-width:768px){ .hh-page-inner{ padding:56px 24px; } .hh-page h1{ font-size:32px; } }
</style>

<div class="hh-page">
  <div class="hh-page-inner">
    <h1>Materials &amp; Care</h1>
    <div class="hh-page-rule"></div>

    <h2>What We Use</h2>
    <span class="hh-mat-badge">18k Gold Vermeil</span>
    <p>Our signature material. 18k gold vermeil is a thick layer of real 18-karat gold electroplated over a sterling silver base. It meets strict quality standards, offering the warmth and brilliance of solid gold at a fraction of the cost.</p>
    <span class="hh-mat-badge">Sterling Silver</span>
    <p>Our base metal is 925 sterling silver, which is 92.5% pure silver. It is hypoallergenic, durable, and an ideal foundation for gold vermeil.</p>
    <span class="hh-mat-badge">Natural Stones</span>
    <p>Select pieces feature genuine natural stones including freshwater pearls, cubic zirconia, and semi-precious gemstones. Each stone is individually set and may show slight natural variation.</p>

    <h2>Care Instructions</h2>
    <p>With the right care, your Humble Hearted pieces will maintain their beauty for years to come.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Remove jewelry before showering, swimming, or exercising.</li>
      <li>Avoid contact with perfume, hairspray, lotions, and cleaning products.</li>
      <li>Wipe gently with a soft, dry cloth after wearing.</li>
      <li>Store each piece separately in an airtight bag or the original packaging to prevent tarnishing and scratching.</li>
      <li>Keep jewelry away from extreme heat and direct sunlight.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Tarnishing</h2>
    <p>All gold-plated jewelry can tarnish over time, especially with exposure to moisture and chemicals. Following our care guidelines will significantly extend the life of your pieces. If tarnishing occurs, a gentle polish with a soft jewelry cloth can restore the shine.</p>
  </div>
</div>
